@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title US11 - System Sequence Diagram (SSD)

autonumber

actor "Product Owner" as PO
participant ":System" as System

activate PO

PO -> System : I intend to register all the operations on the camp book, using \nthe information on the file generated by the watering system simulator.
activate System

"System" --> PO: requests the path of the file to be used

deactivate System

PO -> System : provides the file path requested

activate System

System --> PO : displays a message informing if each operation was/wasn't successfully registered in camp book

deactivate System

@enduml